01:21:46.810 --> 01:21:51.810
I don't know if you are used those things or not at all but you should use in music.

01:21:51.840 --> 01:21:58.372
There are so many things you have which all of these things you should use which helps a lot in music.

01:21:58.420 --> 01:22:03.420
